ABSTRACT
Certain aspects of the present disclosure provide methods
and apparatus for autonomous receive (RX) detection. One
example method for wireless communications generally
includes powering down a portion of a receive path in a first
module; detecting, in a second module comprising another
portion of the receive path, that a radio frequency (RF)
signal has been received by the second module while the
portion of the receive path in the first module is powered
down; and sending a control signal to power up the portion
of the receive path in the first module, based on the detec-
tion.
